aloff 和 Ernesto Ruscio/Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Travis-Scott-Kylie-Jenner-and-Timothee-Chalamet.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Travis-Scott-Kylie-Jenner-and-Timothee-Chalamet-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Travis-Scott-Kylie-Jenner-and-Timothee-Chalamet-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Travis-Scott-Kylie-Jenner-and-Timothee-Chalamet-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Travis-Scott-Kylie-Jenner-and-Timothee-Chalamet-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Travis-Scott-Kylie-Jenner-and-Timothee-Chalamet-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/travis-scott">特拉维斯·斯科特</a>的粉丝一直猜测这位说唱歌手在他的歌曲《Meltdown》中对演员蒂莫西·柴勒梅德进行了侮辱。</p><p>继 2018 年的《Astroworld》之后，斯科特今天（7 月 28 日）终于发行了他期待已久的专辑《Utopia》。在粉丝们开始猜测斯科特（又名 La Flame）可能鄙视了<a href="/artists/drake">Drake</a>后，专辑中以 Drake 为主角的第七首歌曲《Meltdown》在社交媒体上引起了关注。</p><p>在歌曲第二节的结尾，《火焰》提到了查拉梅在即将上映的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wonka"><em>《旺卡》</em></a>中扮演的角色威利·旺卡。</p><p> <em>“包裹奶酪，包裹我，因为我有财产（包裹，奶酪，包裹）/巧克力AP和巧克力Vs（Vs），拥有威利旺卡工厂（Vs）/像卡路里一样燃烧运动员，找到另一个像我一样热的火焰，婊子，”</em>他说唱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Travis Scott - MELTDOWN（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LuKm4L9ryB0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>专辑发行后，粉丝们在 Twitter 上分享了他们对这首歌的看法。“我这辈子从来没想过会看到 Travis Scott 辱骂 Timothee Chalamet，”一位用户分享道。</p><p>另一位补充道：“操，威利·旺卡，我的兄弟们都不会见到威利·旺卡。”</p><p>粉丝们认为，这位说唱歌手之所以对这位演员不屑一顾，是因为柴勒梅德是真人秀明星凯莉·詹纳的绯闻男友。詹纳是斯科特的前夫，两人育有两个孩子，一个是 5 岁的女儿，名叫斯托米，另一个是 13 个月大的女儿，名叫艾尔。</p><p>据报道，斯科特和詹纳今年早些时候宣布退出。据<a href="https://people.com/tv/kylie-jenner-timothee-chalamet-hanging-out-getting-know-each-other/"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>报道，从那时起，她就开始与这位法裔美国演员关系密切。詹纳和斯科特在 2017 年至 2022 年底期间断断续续地约会过。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvOK2-ypmQh/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 5